WEBVTT

1
00:00:01.000 --> 00:00:04.000
{\an8}<b><font color="#9CD5FF">One Pace Premium</font></b>
Keep the project alive: <font color="#a8c7fa">ko-fi.com/not6ip</font>

2
00:01:34.740 --> 00:01:39.030
Mink Pedro, Captain of the Guardians

3
00:01:39.430 --> 00:01:40.590
My leg...

4
00:01:42.530 --> 00:01:44.890
Damn! I can't move!

5
00:01:45.350 --> 00:01:46.270
Chopper-san !

6
00:01:50.000 --> 00:01:51.370
Brook!

7
00:01:53.800 --> 00:01:55.440
You fools...

8
00:01:55.440 --> 00:02:01.030
That candy will slowly
seep into your bodies.

9
00:02:05.700 --> 00:02:09.890
It's no use.
You won't be able to move anymore.

10
00:02:13.650 --> 00:02:14.780
Chopper-san !

11
00:02:16.490 --> 00:02:19.080
Don't panic, don't panic.

12
00:02:19.080 --> 00:02:20.550
Goodness...

13
00:02:21.140 --> 00:02:27.670
What made you think you'd
be able to take your ship back?

14
00:02:27.670 --> 00:02:31.300
In order to catch you guys,

15
00:02:31.300 --> 00:02:35.390
we've mobilized all of our soldiers
across the island

16
00:02:35.390 --> 00:02:39.020
to set up traps at various places.

17
00:02:39.020 --> 00:02:42.570
You cannot escape from us.

18
00:02:43.550 --> 00:02:46.990
The difference in our power is clear!

19
00:02:48.340 --> 00:02:50.490
Damn!

20
00:02:50.490 --> 00:02:54.000
I... I can't even transform!

21
00:02:54.000 --> 00:02:56.000
Let Chopper-san go!

22
00:02:56.000 --> 00:02:58.740
Idiot! It's too late!

23
00:02:58.740 --> 00:03:01.710
This is your punishment for defying me.

24
00:03:01.710 --> 00:03:05.040
I'll turn you into a candy man
and lick you until you're gone.

25
00:03:05.040 --> 00:03:05.980
Lick!

26
00:03:07.280 --> 00:03:10.510
The candy will coat your whole body,

27
00:03:10.510 --> 00:03:13.760
and fill up your entire body
until you can't breathe anymore.

28
00:03:13.760 --> 00:03:16.830
And with that agony...

29
00:03:17.710 --> 00:03:21.360
it will take only three minutes to kill you!

30
00:03:22.870 --> 00:03:23.820
No way...

31
00:03:23.820 --> 00:03:30.080
And then, it will be complete!
A sweet candy man!

32
00:03:36.600 --> 00:03:38.260
Chopper-san !

33
00:03:38.260 --> 00:03:39.920
Stop!

34
00:03:44.450 --> 00:03:47.960
It's too late to regret your choices!

35
00:03:47.960 --> 00:03:50.840
Remember... I gave you a chance!

36
00:03:50.840 --> 00:03:54.680
I offered to let the two of you go.

37
00:03:54.680 --> 00:03:58.100
You guys are clueless!

38
00:03:58.810 --> 00:04:01.100
This island...

39
00:04:01.100 --> 00:04:04.190
isn't sweet at all!

40
00:04:04.720 --> 00:04:07.530
Chopper-san !

41
00:04:08.520 --> 00:04:11.490
Why don't you sit back and count the seconds?

42
00:04:18.080 --> 00:04:21.080
This is exactly what sweet fools such as yourselves deserve...

43
00:04:22.860 --> 00:04:26.500
Oh, stop! I don't wanna get sweetened!

44
00:04:26.500 --> 00:04:28.430
Oh, stop!

45
00:04:30.740 --> 00:04:35.820
I'll turn you into a candy man and lick you!

46
00:04:47.090 --> 00:04:49.150
Hey, Big Brother Peros!

47
00:04:50.300 --> 00:04:51.730
That's Mama...

48
00:04:51.730 --> 00:04:55.620
Wedding...

49
00:04:56.100 --> 00:04:58.710
She's still on her ravenous rampage...

50
00:04:58.710 --> 00:05:01.440
...cake!

51
00:05:02.650 --> 00:05:06.500
We need to lure her to Cacao Island
where Pudding is waiting.

52
00:05:06.500 --> 00:05:11.300
If she finds out there's no cake
on this ship, she'll kill me.

53
00:05:16.260 --> 00:05:19.080
I don't think we're at that stage yet.

54
00:05:22.810 --> 00:05:25.480
Let me eat!

55
00:05:37.480 --> 00:05:39.870
Cake!

56
00:05:39.880 --> 00:05:42.670
It's the coast! Get to the Sunny !

57
00:05:44.440 --> 00:05:47.250
He's still alive? Straw Hat...

58
00:05:47.890 --> 00:05:50.800
Our soldiers must've been the ones
wiped out by the lightning...

59
00:05:54.330 --> 00:05:55.390
Who are those guys?!

60
00:05:55.840 --> 00:05:58.180
They've hijacked the ship!

61
00:05:58.180 --> 00:06:00.770
What? Brook?! Chopper?!

62
00:06:00.770 --> 00:06:02.020
What's that?!

63
00:06:03.960 --> 00:06:05.710
Get back to the Mirro-world.

64
00:06:07.050 --> 00:06:09.690
If you stay,

65
00:06:09.690 --> 00:06:12.820
you'll be lying at his feet in a few seconds.

66
00:06:15.180 --> 00:06:17.450
Jump into the mirror!

67
00:06:17.450 --> 00:06:21.950
Perospero and Katakuri...
Those two of all others...

68
00:06:21.950 --> 00:06:24.330
The disaster continues!

69
00:06:26.690 --> 00:06:32.040
It's amazing that you got this far...
I'm impressed.

70
00:06:33.300 --> 00:06:37.550
But you're going to a graveyard now!

71
00:06:37.550 --> 00:06:40.270
This is where you all must die!

72
00:06:48.460 --> 00:06:50.730
Candy Maiden!

73
00:06:50.730 --> 00:06:52.240
A wall of candy!

74
00:06:52.240 --> 00:06:56.570
It's obvious that it's not just a wall!

75
00:07:02.040 --> 00:07:04.080
Fishman Karate...

76
00:07:04.400 --> 00:07:06.330
Gum-Gum...

77
00:07:08.110 --> 00:07:10.250
Shark Tile Fist!

78
00:07:10.250 --> 00:07:12.590
Jet Bazooka!

79
00:07:15.800 --> 00:07:16.970
Yes!

80
00:07:18.900 --> 00:07:20.460
Not yet, not yet...

81
00:07:20.460 --> 00:07:23.800
Don't underestimate me!

82
00:07:24.750 --> 00:07:26.310
Huh? What is it?!

83
00:07:29.750 --> 00:07:31.980
Candy Maiden...

84
00:07:32.550 --> 00:07:34.400
Decoration!

85
00:07:35.180 --> 00:07:37.260
It's gigantic...

86
00:07:37.990 --> 00:07:39.740
This is the end!

87
00:07:45.440 --> 00:07:47.330
No one can get through here!

88
00:07:49.820 --> 00:07:51.590
Go around and get to the ship!

89
00:07:53.460 --> 00:07:55.360
No, run straight!

90
00:07:59.890 --> 00:08:02.320
Gum-Gum...

91
00:08:06.230 --> 00:08:08.540
Red Hawk!

92
00:08:17.400 --> 00:08:18.800
Is that a flame?!

93
00:08:58.240 --> 00:09:01.160
His powers are just like Luffy's!

94
00:09:20.130 --> 00:09:23.050
Wedding...

95
00:09:24.800 --> 00:09:28.480
cake!

96
00:09:33.060 --> 00:09:34.230
Here she comes!

97
00:09:38.260 --> 00:09:40.820
What should we do, Luffy?!
We're surrounded!

98
00:09:40.820 --> 00:09:44.010
Luffy! Force Katakuri off the ship!

99
00:09:44.010 --> 00:09:46.100
We'll find a way to set sail!

100
00:09:46.100 --> 00:09:47.640
I got it!

101
00:09:47.640 --> 00:09:50.260
– This way!
– Okay!

102
00:09:52.710 --> 00:09:55.810
That bastard!
He must've come from the mirror dimension!

103
00:09:59.480 --> 00:10:05.400
Wedding cake!

104
00:10:06.170 --> 00:10:10.250
I don't want to be in the path
of Mama's ravenous rampage.

105
00:10:10.250 --> 00:10:11.570
Lick.

106
00:10:12.680 --> 00:10:15.230
Armament: Hardening!

107
00:10:17.280 --> 00:10:20.000
Gum-Gum...

108
00:10:22.050 --> 00:10:25.260
Hawk Gatling!

109
00:10:37.870 --> 00:10:40.910
Why?! I'm using haki, but I can't hit him!

110
00:10:53.360 --> 00:10:55.920
Chopper! Brook! Are you all right?!

111
00:10:55.920 --> 00:10:57.090
Stay with us!

112
00:11:00.240 --> 00:11:03.260
Where is it?

113
00:11:03.260 --> 00:11:05.680
The cake!

114
00:11:10.790 --> 00:11:11.810
Carrot.

115
00:11:13.600 --> 00:11:15.600
Try not to be startled by this sudden turn of events.

116
00:11:15.600 --> 00:11:16.360
What?

117
00:11:17.260 --> 00:11:18.860
I have a suspicion...

118
00:11:18.860 --> 00:11:20.990
that Luffy and his crew...

119
00:11:20.990 --> 00:11:23.570
are the ones that our people...

120
00:11:23.570 --> 00:11:27.330
and the Kozuki family have been
awaiting for centuries.

121
00:11:27.330 --> 00:11:31.210
The ones who will guide us
to the new dawn!

122
00:11:31.210 --> 00:11:32.670
For centuries?!

123
00:11:44.500 --> 00:11:47.640
Hey, Mont d'Or, can you hear me?

124
00:11:47.640 --> 00:11:49.870
Yeah, I can hear you.

125
00:11:49.870 --> 00:11:55.400
Surround Whole Cake Island's
southwestern coast with battleships.

126
00:11:55.400 --> 00:11:58.030
Right away, Brother Peros!

127
00:11:59.020 --> 00:12:01.770
I guess Straw Hat and the others
are still alive.

128
00:12:04.160 --> 00:12:05.660
A Coup de...

129
00:12:06.070 --> 00:12:07.440
What?!

130
00:12:07.440 --> 00:12:11.760
Coup de Burst!
This ship is capable of flying a kilometer away!

131
00:12:11.760 --> 00:12:15.830
If we try to just set sail,
Big Mom will sink us in no time!

132
00:12:15.830 --> 00:12:19.600
I don't really understand,
but this is the best way to escape, right?

133
00:12:19.600 --> 00:12:20.300
Yeah!

134
00:12:20.300 --> 00:12:23.430
Okay! Then let's bet on it!

135
00:12:24.930 --> 00:12:26.800
Big Mom is coming!

136
00:12:26.820 --> 00:12:29.260
There you are!

137
00:12:29.910 --> 00:12:32.910
Carrot! You go help them
get ready to set sail!

138
00:12:32.910 --> 00:12:33.700
What?

139
00:12:33.700 --> 00:12:34.720
Hurry up!

140
00:12:34.720 --> 00:12:36.350
Okay!

141
00:12:41.170 --> 00:12:44.220
Is it there?

142
00:12:44.220 --> 00:12:47.610
The wedding cake?!

143
00:12:53.100 --> 00:12:57.280
Hey, Brook, Chopper!
Stay with me!

144
00:12:57.280 --> 00:13:01.540
Even if we make it out of here,
it'll be meaningless if you two die!

145
00:13:03.700 --> 00:13:07.590
We spotted the Straw Hats
at the southwest coast!

146
00:13:07.590 --> 00:13:11.100
This is Minister Amande aboard the Nuts Island tarte.

147
00:13:11.100 --> 00:13:13.210
We'll corner Straw Hat and the others.

148
00:13:21.920 --> 00:13:23.410
This is terrible.

149
00:13:23.410 --> 00:13:27.190
Battleships are coming from the sea,
and Big Mom from the land.

150
00:13:27.190 --> 00:13:29.770
We're completely trapped in the middle!

151
00:13:37.310 --> 00:13:39.740
Nami! We have to set sail!

152
00:13:39.740 --> 00:13:44.120
I know! But I have to load
two more barrels of cola!

153
00:13:44.120 --> 00:13:48.240
I'll load the rest. You go prepare
for the Coup-de-whatever!

154
00:13:48.240 --> 00:13:50.280
All right, I'll leave it to you, then!

155
00:14:07.900 --> 00:14:10.950
Candy Wave!

156
00:14:21.180 --> 00:14:22.500
What?!

157
00:14:23.850 --> 00:14:25.160
Candy?!

158
00:14:25.160 --> 00:14:28.750
Oh no! There's no way we can use the Coup de Burst like this!

159
00:14:37.860 --> 00:14:39.250
What's wrong?!

160
00:14:39.250 --> 00:14:42.600
This is bad!
The Sunny has been trapped by candy!

161
00:14:42.610 --> 00:14:43.520
What?!

162
00:14:47.480 --> 00:14:51.020
Did you see the power of my Candy Wave?!

163
00:14:51.020 --> 00:14:53.820
I'm a perfectionist!

164
00:14:53.820 --> 00:14:55.570
Oh, there he is!

165
00:14:58.070 --> 00:14:59.700
What should we do?

166
00:14:59.700 --> 00:15:03.660
Turn Brook and Chopper back,
as well as the ship, candy jerk!

167
00:15:06.160 --> 00:15:07.540
If nothing is done...

168
00:15:07.540 --> 00:15:10.710
Cake!

169
00:15:10.710 --> 00:15:13.420
You'll either be destroyed by Mama

170
00:15:13.420 --> 00:15:17.120
or destroyed by our cannons!

171
00:15:30.090 --> 00:15:35.820
Either way, your chance of survival is zero!

172
00:16:10.850 --> 00:16:13.100
Beast Sword: Imperial Guardian Lion!

173
00:16:23.510 --> 00:16:27.690
Hey, do you know what my bounty is?

174
00:16:27.690 --> 00:16:29.370
It's 700 million.

175
00:16:30.870 --> 00:16:34.920
A weakling like you has
no chance of defeating me.

176
00:16:45.430 --> 00:16:49.230
You escaped death. Lick.

177
00:16:50.690 --> 00:16:55.580
It's pointless to die here!
The day of the new dawn is coming!

178
00:16:55.580 --> 00:16:57.790
I must go back to my country!

179
00:17:00.170 --> 00:17:02.630
You're so handsome.

180
00:17:02.630 --> 00:17:05.670
I'll reduce it to 50 years.

181
00:17:05.670 --> 00:17:07.550
Go on with your life.

182
00:17:09.290 --> 00:17:10.800
At that time,

183
00:17:10.800 --> 00:17:16.350
if you hadn't sacrificed your left eye,
you would've been killed for sure...

184
00:17:17.880 --> 00:17:20.720
Did you want to survive that badly?

185
00:17:22.370 --> 00:17:23.980
All right...

186
00:17:23.980 --> 00:17:26.930
How old are you right now?

187
00:17:26.930 --> 00:17:28.480
I'm 27...

188
00:17:28.480 --> 00:17:35.120
So 50 years of your life were drained away,
meaning it's more like you've lived 77 years.

189
00:17:36.870 --> 00:17:40.580
Now, I wonder how many years
you expect to live...

190
00:17:42.110 --> 00:17:45.460
At the very least,
I'd like to choose where I die.

191
00:17:47.200 --> 00:17:48.470
By the way,

192
00:17:48.470 --> 00:17:52.850
you were the captain of the Nox Pirates...

193
00:17:52.850 --> 00:17:56.810
"Nox" means "night," right?

194
00:17:56.810 --> 00:17:59.140
That sounds pretty negative.

195
00:17:59.650 --> 00:18:01.980
They say, "Every night comes to an end."

196
00:18:03.110 --> 00:18:04.290
And...

197
00:18:05.430 --> 00:18:08.190
"nox" is the same as...

198
00:18:09.680 --> 00:18:11.600
"just before dawn."

199
00:18:13.190 --> 00:18:14.800
If I can serve as the foundation for

200
00:18:14.800 --> 00:18:17.790
the new dawn that Master
and the others are hoping for,

201
00:18:17.790 --> 00:18:19.210
then I'll have accomplished what I want most.

202
00:18:20.610 --> 00:18:23.290
I think I have enough time for that...

203
00:18:27.300 --> 00:18:33.930
You once said that "just before the dawn"
and "nox" meant the same thing...

204
00:18:33.930 --> 00:18:40.440
But the only thing that's waiting for you
is the eternal darkness known as death.

205
00:18:40.440 --> 00:18:41.280
No...

206
00:18:50.680 --> 00:18:54.370
Roger! Lord Oden! I'm beggin' you, take me along!

207
00:18:56.400 --> 00:18:59.870
I'll do anything! Take me with you!

208
00:19:02.120 --> 00:19:05.760
Kid, you still have to wait.

209
00:19:05.760 --> 00:19:08.520
I'm not a kid, I'm Pedro!

210
00:19:14.170 --> 00:19:17.190
My time is limited.

211
00:19:17.190 --> 00:19:22.690
Listen! Everyone gets their own turn.

212
00:19:24.220 --> 00:19:26.320
Be patient and wait!

213
00:19:26.320 --> 00:19:31.950
It'll come naturally. Your turn, I mean...

214
00:19:33.060 --> 00:19:36.200
Goodbye, Pedro.

215
00:19:37.530 --> 00:19:40.200
I understand, Roger!

216
00:19:50.300 --> 00:19:52.750
Pedro!

217
00:19:52.750 --> 00:19:54.010
Roger...

218
00:19:54.020 --> 00:19:55.930
What about Roger?

219
00:19:59.760 --> 00:20:01.220
They're saying he died!

220
00:20:03.810 --> 00:20:08.920
Roger said, "Everyone gets their own turn"!

221
00:20:08.920 --> 00:20:10.920
What are you talking about?

222
00:20:10.920 --> 00:20:12.750
This is my turn!

223
00:20:15.660 --> 00:20:19.220
This will break all of your magic spells, right?

224
00:20:19.960 --> 00:20:21.140
Bombs?!

225
00:20:21.140 --> 00:20:24.880
Stop, you fool!
What do you think you're doing?!

226
00:20:25.380 --> 00:20:27.100
Let go of me!

227
00:20:31.760 --> 00:20:33.720
I...

228
00:20:33.050 --> 00:20:33.720
Huh?

229
00:20:34.220 --> 00:20:37.240
had a feeling that this
would be my last journey.

230
00:20:37.240 --> 00:20:39.310
What do you mean, Pedro?

231
00:20:45.420 --> 00:20:46.370
Pedro?!

232
00:20:47.400 --> 00:20:48.660
Farewell.

233
00:21:18.220 --> 00:21:20.280
What do you mean, Pedro?

234
00:21:20.280 --> 00:21:24.200
One day, you'll see how important it was...

235
00:21:24.690 --> 00:21:29.480
to allow Luffy and the others to set sail!

236
00:21:33.490 --> 00:21:36.210
Pedro!

237
00:21:37.370 --> 00:21:38.920
Listen!

238
00:21:38.920 --> 00:21:42.000
You-gara must press on!

239
00:21:42.000 --> 00:21:43.760
Pedro!

240
00:21:44.460 --> 00:21:47.180
Don't tell me Big Bro Peros is...

241
00:21:51.260 --> 00:21:55.320
Oh, no! Mama and Commander Perospero

242
00:21:55.320 --> 00:21:58.020
were caught in the explosion!

243
00:22:10.190 --> 00:22:13.500
That candy he produced is starting to melt!

244
00:22:18.080 --> 00:22:20.900
I can't believe he sacrificed himself...

245
00:22:20.900 --> 00:22:23.630
How could you do that, Pedro!

246
00:22:36.720 --> 00:22:39.240
I thought I was done for!

247
00:22:39.240 --> 00:22:41.400
Are you guys all right?!

248
00:22:48.940 --> 00:22:50.420
Stop, Carrot!

249
00:22:50.420 --> 00:22:55.130
Let go of me! Let me go back to where Pedro was!
Maybe he's still alive!

250
00:22:55.130 --> 00:23:00.150
No! You saw that explosion...
He saved us!

251
00:23:00.150 --> 00:23:03.900
We had no chance to survive until now!

252
00:23:03.900 --> 00:23:07.540
You have to understand why Pedro
did what he did! Please!

253
00:23:10.710 --> 00:23:13.140
Ready to fly, Nami?!

254
00:23:13.960 --> 00:23:15.770
Yes, it's all set!

255
00:23:15.770 --> 00:23:19.300
Chopper! Brook! Are you with us?

256
00:23:20.350 --> 00:23:21.500
Oh?

257
00:23:21.500 --> 00:23:22.700
Jinbe!

258
00:23:22.700 --> 00:23:25.280
Yes, they're with us!

259
00:23:26.020 --> 00:23:28.240
Set sail, you guys!

260
00:23:35.110 --> 00:23:37.620
If we waste this moment,

261
00:23:37.620 --> 00:23:40.330
then Pedro would be ashamed of us!

262
00:23:40.330 --> 00:23:43.630
We'll escape from here no matter what!

263
00:23:49.960 --> 00:23:51.800
At any cost!

264
00:23:53.670 --> 00:23:55.600
Why is everyone...

265
00:23:56.720 --> 00:23:59.020
so heated up?

266
00:24:01.760 --> 00:24:04.540
Get out of here, Big Mom Pirates!

267
00:24:04.540 --> 00:24:05.610
Carrot!

268
00:24:23.530 --> 00:24:25.150
Oops...

269
00:24:26.030 --> 00:24:30.250
Get up! Get on your feet, Carrot!
And take the sword!

270
00:24:30.250 --> 00:24:33.140
She has no aptitude for swords.

271
00:24:33.140 --> 00:24:35.650
Pedro! This is none of your business!

272
00:24:35.650 --> 00:24:38.940
Carrot will become a strong swordswoman
under my guidance.

273
00:24:38.940 --> 00:24:45.020
There is more than one way to get stronger.
There must be a way that's better suited for her.

274
00:24:47.110 --> 00:24:48.520
What is this?

275
00:24:50.720 --> 00:24:52.270
Take a fighting pose.

276
00:24:54.770 --> 00:24:57.610
That suits you much better.

277
00:25:03.030 --> 00:25:06.310
You are capable of floating
in the air for a while.

278
00:25:06.310 --> 00:25:12.770
If you take advantage of that and Electro, you can
acquire your own strength and way of fighting.

279
00:25:12.770 --> 00:25:13.920
Are you sure?

280
00:25:14.160 --> 00:25:15.490
Yes.

281
00:25:15.490 --> 00:25:18.770
Come at me!
I'll be your training partner.

282
00:25:18.770 --> 00:25:20.300
All right!

283
00:25:33.900 --> 00:25:37.080
I thought I couldn't become strong.

284
00:25:37.080 --> 00:25:40.840
I can't believe there's a skill suited for me.

285
00:25:40.840 --> 00:25:43.720
It's all thanks to you, Pedro.

286
00:25:43.720 --> 00:25:46.050
It doesn't matter how you fight.

287
00:25:46.050 --> 00:25:49.880
From now on, you must be a strong fighter
and be constantly prepared.

288
00:25:52.250 --> 00:25:55.840
Everyone gets their own turn.

289
00:25:58.110 --> 00:26:00.210
Don't worry...

290
00:26:10.180 --> 00:26:11.600
Electrical...

291
00:26:18.950 --> 00:26:22.910
As long as I'm here, you will not set sail!

292
00:26:31.300 --> 00:26:33.750
Get away from Carrot!

293
00:26:40.370 --> 00:26:42.490
Carrot! Leave him to me!

294
00:26:43.380 --> 00:26:44.890
Luffy...

295
00:26:50.470 --> 00:26:53.190
I hope you're strong enough to force me out...

296
00:26:58.180 --> 00:27:02.590
We'll set sail!
I'm the captain of this ship!

297
00:27:02.590 --> 00:27:06.200
Gum-Gum Elephant Gun!

298
00:27:17.940 --> 00:27:19.520
The sails can stay like that.

299
00:27:20.790 --> 00:27:23.470
Toward the northwest, Coup de Burst!

300
00:27:23.470 --> 00:27:26.010
Azimuth: 45 degrees to the northwest!

301
00:27:26.010 --> 00:27:27.630
I see...

302
00:27:27.630 --> 00:27:31.010
I certainly can't attack the others
if you do that.

303
00:27:31.010 --> 00:27:34.720
This way, you can't stop it
even if you know what'll happen!

304
00:27:36.080 --> 00:27:38.170
Brother! I'm here to save you!

305
00:27:41.180 --> 00:27:43.130
We'll avenge Big Bro Peros!

306
00:27:43.130 --> 00:27:46.910
All ships, prepare to fire
toward the enemy ship!

307
00:27:46.910 --> 00:27:48.760
Adjust the cannon's shot!

308
00:27:49.390 --> 00:27:51.550
Shark-chan, come back!

309
00:27:53.140 --> 00:27:59.290
Chopper-san, can you grab it on that side? Let's pull it
close to the Sunny before they start shooting!

310
00:27:59.290 --> 00:28:02.520
Carrot! Hang on. Can you get up?

311
00:28:02.520 --> 00:28:06.000
Yes... Nami, thank you.

312
00:28:08.800 --> 00:28:11.620
Where is it?!

313
00:28:11.620 --> 00:28:12.820
Big Mom!

314
00:28:12.820 --> 00:28:18.020
We're really in trouble now!
We have to escape before the ship is destroyed!

315
00:28:24.900 --> 00:28:29.470
Is that... Pedro?! Is he alive?!

316
00:28:42.290 --> 00:28:45.800
Damn! Pedro, that bastard!

317
00:28:45.800 --> 00:28:47.150
That's not Pedro!

318
00:28:47.150 --> 00:28:48.530
No...

319
00:28:48.530 --> 00:28:51.750
Oh, man... I felt my blood going cold...

320
00:28:51.750 --> 00:28:55.350
My Candy Armor was completely destroyed!

321
00:28:57.850 --> 00:29:02.440
No way... Why is he alive?!

322
00:29:04.310 --> 00:29:07.590
It looks like all of the second round shots
were intercepted!

323
00:29:07.590 --> 00:29:10.570
Third round! Hurry up and load!

324
00:29:11.990 --> 00:29:14.930
L-Let go of me!

325
00:29:14.930 --> 00:29:16.500
Nami! Carrot!

326
00:29:17.240 --> 00:29:18.610
Jinbe!

327
00:29:18.610 --> 00:29:20.030
Brook!

328
00:29:20.030 --> 00:29:21.580
Chopper!

329
00:29:38.140 --> 00:29:39.730
Listen to me!

330
00:29:40.220 --> 00:29:43.940
I'll be back! I'll leave the rest to you!

331
00:29:43.940 --> 00:29:46.280
What?! What do you mean by that?!

332
00:29:49.360 --> 00:29:54.100
When the lever returns to its original position,
the burst is ready!

333
00:29:54.100 --> 00:29:56.970
All right, everyone! Hang onto something!

334
00:29:56.970 --> 00:29:58.270
I got it!

335
00:29:58.270 --> 00:30:00.730
We're ready anytime!

336
00:30:00.730 --> 00:30:02.260
We're ready too!

337
00:30:04.170 --> 00:30:05.720
Okay, here we go!

338
00:30:07.090 --> 00:30:09.890
Don't let the Straw Hats get away! Fire!

339
00:30:13.300 --> 00:30:14.240
Now!

340
00:30:14.240 --> 00:30:17.900
Everybody! Don't forget to shout it!

341
00:30:17.900 --> 00:30:21.140
Coup de...

342
00:30:23.400 --> 00:30:26.450
Burst!

343
00:30:46.400 --> 00:30:48.000
This is Amande.

344
00:30:48.000 --> 00:30:51.170
The enemy ship flew into the sky.

345
00:30:51.170 --> 00:30:52.460
The sky?!

346
00:30:56.280 --> 00:30:58.420
Hey, where's Luffy?!

347
00:31:03.210 --> 00:31:04.700
That's Straw Hat!

348
00:31:04.700 --> 00:31:05.850
Run!

349
00:31:11.980 --> 00:31:16.400
Mirro-world

350
00:31:17.600 --> 00:31:19.400
You succeeded...

351
00:31:20.100 --> 00:31:22.860
Here, I can beat you up as much as I want!

352
00:31:26.190 --> 00:31:27.700
The path to the ship!

353
00:31:27.700 --> 00:31:29.750
He destroyed it himself!

354
00:31:41.540 --> 00:31:45.510
So this is your determination as captain...

355
00:31:46.370 --> 00:31:49.530
But... you are no match for me.

356
00:31:49.530 --> 00:31:52.350
This is where you will die.

357
00:31:52.350 --> 00:31:55.080
I'll return to the Sunny...

358
00:31:55.080 --> 00:31:57.310
as soon as I take you down!
